{
  "title": "LiteLLM Overview",
  "description": "## LiteLLM\n\nLiteLLM is a lightweight, flexible LLM proxy and management layer. This dashboard provides real-time insights into API key and team quotas, deployment health, proxy performance, latency, token usage, endpoint health, and more.\n\n**Further reading:**\n- [LiteLLM GitHub](https://github.com/BerriAI/litellm)\n- [LiteLLM Docs](https://docs.litellm.ai/)",
